window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I always wanted a little sister. But not her.</p> <p>The cult known as the Black Phoenix is hot on my tail, attempting to thwart me as I liberate monster women across the multiverse and bring them back to my castle. Worse yet, a half-sister I never knew I had is their champion.</p> <p>The only thing that can stop a Van Helsing is a Van Helsing, so I can’t afford to take her lightly. What’s more, I have to stay focused on my mission. But when there’s downtime…</p> <p>Well, it doesn’t hurt to have a little fun.</p>"; 
